strings: <voice_0x010015EF><se_low>the force: That's right, uncle... loathsome... philosopher!
<voice_0x010015F0><se_low>the force: Do you have the courage to stone me? which ones ! Besides
<voice_0x010015F1><se_low>the force: Remind me how long it will take me to unseal your poor thing!
<voice_0x010015F2><se_low>the force: Feel a presence? Catch the champion!
<voice_0x010015F3><se_low>the force: So I did not stop! Make sure there is enough room on the side.
<voice_0x010015F4><se_low>the force: Shaman Shaman! Human killer! Saint died!
<voice_0x010015F5><se_low>the force: Say yes. Who are you
<voice_0x010015F6><se_low>the force: What are people doing on my website?
<voice_0x010015F7><se_low>the force: ...Anyone who tries to live an unhappy life will be disappointed.
<voice_0x010015F8><se_low>the force: However, the trip was not spoiled. Enjoy it till the cursed holy man is gone!
